Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.13,0:17:47.96,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,だって　私は私だから
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.67,0:17:53.30,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,これでいいってこと？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.51,0:17:59.14,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,もしかして　生徒Aって何か設定ある子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.06,0:18:01.06,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,ある子です
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.56,0:18:02.81,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,マジですか
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.06,0:18:03.85,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,はい
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.85,0:18:06.02,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,連載では描いてないんですが
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.61,0:18:10.57,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,そっか　この表情はそれか
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.19,0:18:13.40,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,もういっぺん　今のとこ聞けますか
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.66,0:18:15.03,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,はい　流します
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.58,0:18:22.79,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,またね　ツバキ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.25,0:18:26.33,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,陽菜　自分なんかやっちゃったかな
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.33,0:18:28.67,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,たぶん私じゃないかな
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.67,0:18:30.42,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,それか2人とも
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.42,0:18:33.88,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,だって　私は私だから
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.18,0:18:37.76,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,なるほどね
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.05,0:18:41.64,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,この2人には連載で語られてない接点があったんですか
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.02,0:18:42.73,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,はい
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.06,0:18:45.35,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,ツバキはこの子と知り合うことで
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.35,0:18:47.56,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,ブルームボールの魅力に目覚めて
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.94,0:18:51.78,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,あと　実はツバキの理論家の設定も　ある意味…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.78,0:18:54.32,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,すいません　こちらの説明不足で
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.61,0:18:55.57,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,いやいや
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.57,0:18:58.87,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,私がもうちょっと原作から読み取ってればよかったんです
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.41,0:19:00.62,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,こっちのミスですよ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.62,0:19:01.41,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,申し訳ない
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.00,0:19:02.79,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,いえ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.12,0:19:06.12,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,私全然こだわってなかったんです
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.58,0:19:07.63,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,さっきまで
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.13,0:19:11.71,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,ああ　今ので
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.34,0:19:14.01,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,はい　今ので
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.05,0:19:16.97,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,ありますよね　そういうの
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.18,0:19:18.97,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,あります
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.72,0:19:22.06,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,それで　これでオッケーってこと？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.31,0:19:22.85,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,はい
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.31,0:19:25.02,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,いえ　録り直しましょう
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.27,0:19:26.27,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,録るの？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.48,0:19:27.19,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,そう
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.19,0:19:29.36,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,もう一度ちゃんと　いいですか
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.19,0:19:31.40,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,お任せします
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.36,0:19:34.78,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,カット18からのツバキと生徒A
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.78,0:19:37.36,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,ひゃい　すすす…　すいません
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.36,0:19:39.49,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,演技やり過ぎちゃいました？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.28,0:19:42.20,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,いや　やり過ぎてないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.83,0:19:44.20,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,その方向で正解
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.25,0:19:46.25,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,正解？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.25,0:19:46.92,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,監督
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.54,0:19:49.08,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,ツバキと生徒A
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.33,0:19:52.13,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,さっきの感じで　もっと気持ち込めていこう
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.34,0:19:53.76,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,尺は気にしないで
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.76,0:19:55.51,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,あとからこっちで合わすから
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.17,0:19:57.72,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,さっきの感じ？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.09,0:20:00.22,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,もっと気持ち込めて…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.68,0:20:01.51,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,分かった？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.80,0:20:02.51,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,はい
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.35,0:20:05.68,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,このシーンのカット　俺に回しといて
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.98,0:20:06.94,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,分かりました
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.81,0:20:09.90,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,カット18から
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.02,0:20:11.77,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,テイク2
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.78,0:20:20.62,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,またね　ツバキ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.45,0:20:24.20,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,ツバキなら　あっちでも絶対…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.62,0:20:26.91,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,大丈夫だよ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.00,0:20:30.79,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,もちろん
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.50,0:20:34.88,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,だって　私は私だから
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.60,0:20:49.64,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,はい　オーケーです
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.64,0:20:50.52,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,頂きます
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.94,0:20:52.98,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,舞花ちゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.15,0:20:53.82,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,陽菜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.19,0:20:54.94,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,次
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.94,0:20:57.82,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,戻ってカット13からのアヤメ　別録り
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.44,0:20:59.03,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,はい
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.32,0:21:02.07,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,ありがとうございました
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.62,0:21:07.12,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,もう心配させないでよね
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.70,0:21:11.33,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,でも　2人の演技はとってもよかったと思います
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.67,0:21:13.92,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,声優っていいな
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.42,0:21:16.50,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,そうだね
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.71,0:21:18.84,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,はい　オーケーです
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.26,0:21:20.80,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,以上でAパート終わりです
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.68,0:21:24.26,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,ありがとうございました
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.47,0:21:28.43,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,ありがとうございます
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.43,0:21:29.23,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,お疲れさまです
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.81,0:21:31.39,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,ねえ　早かった
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.73,0:21:36.94,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,アフレコって疲れるんだな
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.36,0:21:40.11,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,私もヘロヘロ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.40,0:21:42.82,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,陽菜　それ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.66,0:21:46.28,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,台本がヘロヘロ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.29,0:21:49.91,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,でも…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.79,0:21:52.08,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,楽しかったね
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.08,0:21:54.33,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,うん　最高に楽しかった
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.42,0:22:05.09,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,ここが私の　夢見た場所
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.14,0:22:07.68,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,ケイちゃん　思い出したんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.39,0:22:09.89,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,もともと忘れてない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.14,0:22:11.93,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,そっか
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.52,0:22:14.02,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,名前　なんだっけ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.90,0:22:18.73,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,モモミ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.94,0:22:22.57,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,梅ノ木モモミ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.08,0:23:58.75,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,次回　「向かい風を捕まえて」
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Dialogue Chinese
Dialogue: 1,0:00:02.11,0:00:03.98,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,多谢款待
Dialogue: 1,0:00:04.94,0:00:06.36,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,太好吃了
Dialogue: 1,0:00:06.69,0:00:09.24,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,大家喜欢就好
Dialogue: 1,0:00:09.24,0:00:10.57,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,饭后的茶来了
Dialogue: 1,0:00:11.41,0:00:12.32,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 1,0:00:13.95,0:00:15.41,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,好香
Dialogue: 1,0:00:15.41,0:00:16.54,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,是焙茶吧
Dialogue: 1,0:00:16.83,0:00:19.37,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,宿舍生活也渐渐习惯了
Dialogue: 1,0:00:19.71,0:00:20.50,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 1,0:00:20.92,0:00:22.75,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,虽然房间有点小
Dialogue: 1,0:00:23.09,0:00:25.96,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,只是你添置了太多健身用品吧
Dialogue: 1,0:00:26.30,0:00:28.55,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,全都是我需要的啊
Dialogue: 1,0:00:28.80,0:00:31.09,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,我反而觉得床比较碍事
Dialogue: 1,0:00:31.80,0:00:33.43,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,那你要睡在哪里啊
Dialogue: 1,0:00:34.01,0:00:37.89,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,真是的 我光是因为单人房间就感动得不行了
Dialogue: 1,0:00:38.23,0:00:40.35,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,我喜欢和室
Dialogue: 1,0:00:40.77,0:00:43.11,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,榻榻米上要有被炉
Dialogue: 1,0:00:43.48,0:00:45.61,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,我一定得是木地板
Dialogue: 1,0:00:45.94,0:00:47.32,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,阳菜呢
Dialogue: 1,0:00:48.78,0:00:49.70,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,阳菜？
Dialogue: 1,0:00:51.49,0:00:53.49,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,舞花 怎么了
Dialogue: 1,0:00:53.87,0:00:55.53,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,在说自己的房间
Dialogue: 1,0:00:55.66,0:00:56.45,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,你住习惯了吗
Dialogue: 1,0:00:57.91,0:00:58.91,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,已经习惯啦
Dialogue: 1,0:00:59.12,0:01:00.29,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,嗯 差不多
Dialogue: 1,0:01:00.66,0:01:01.87,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,什么差不多
Dialogue: 1,0:01:04.00,0:01:05.80,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,有人回来了
Dialogue: 1,0:01:07.17,0:01:08.84,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,欢… 欢迎回来
Dialogue: 1,0:01:09.30,0:01:11.01,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,我… 我回来了
Dialogue: 1,0:01:12.38,0:01:13.64,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,要吃晚饭吗
Dialogue: 1,0:01:13.64,0:01:14.93,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,不用了
Dialogue: 1,0:01:14.93,0:01:16.56,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,我们买了便当
Dialogue: 1,0:01:20.52,0:01:21.60,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,好困
Dialogue: 1,0:01:21.81,0:01:24.65,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,别 睡在这里会感冒的
Dialogue: 1,0:01:24.86,0:01:25.94,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,回房间吧
Dialogue: 1,0:01:29.11,0:01:31.15,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,没… 没事吧？
Dialogue: 1,0:01:32.20,0:01:33.78,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,没事没事
Dialogue: 1,0:01:35.24,0:01:36.62,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,晚安
Dialogue: 1,0:01:38.54,0:01:40.58,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,最近每天都这样啊
Dialogue: 1,0:01:41.00,0:01:43.83,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,说明训练课很严格吧
Dialogue: 1,0:01:44.13,0:01:45.21,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 1,0:01:45.71,0:01:48.21,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,我们也来练习吧
Dialogue: 1,0:01:48.42,0:01:51.47,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,也对 距离正式录音只剩两天了
Dialogue: 1,0:01:51.67,0:01:52.55,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,没有异议
Dialogue: 1,0:01:52.88,0:01:53.55,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,阳菜也来…
Dialogue: 1,0:01:54.22,0:01:54.84,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 1,0:01:55.22,0:01:56.10,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,消失了
Dialogue: 1,0:03:47.50,0:03:48.92,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,阳菜 你回来了
Dialogue: 1,0:03:49.46,0:03:50.96,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,我… 我回来了
Dialogue: 1,0:03:51.46,0:03:53.09,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,为什么突然出门了
Dialogue: 1,0:03:53.55,0:03:55.97,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,去便利店买了点东西
Dialogue: 1,0:03:56.17,0:03:57.63,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,要一起练习吗？
Dialogue: 1,0:03:58.59,0:04:00.55,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,那个 我先回趟房间
Dialogue: 1,0:04:01.18,0:04:03.47,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,咦 你还买了卷心菜啊
Dialogue: 1,0:04:05.35,0:04:06.85,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,突然想吃了
Dialogue: 1,0:04:07.23,0:04:09.10,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,就这样整颗吃吗
Dialogue: 1,0:04:09.10,0:04:10.15,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,而且还是在房间？
Dialogue: 1,0:04:10.40,0:04:11.19,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,一个人吃？
Dialogue: 1,0:04:11.69,0:04:13.07,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,是… 是的
Dialogue: 1,0:04:13.36,0:04:15.23,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,最近蔬菜摄入不足
Dialogue: 1,0:04:15.61,0:04:16.53,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,可疑
Dialogue: 1,0:04:16.94,0:04:18.32,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,你在隐瞒什么
Dialogue: 1,0:04:18.70,0:04:20.70,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,没有隐瞒呀
Dialogue: 1,0:04:20.70,0:04:21.78,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,先… 先走了
Dialogue: 1,0:04:22.32,0:04:23.24,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,阳菜
Dialogue: 1,0:04:23.95,0:04:25.74,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,都写在脸上了
Dialogue: 1,0:04:26.29,0:04:28.25,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,怎么样 要去确认吗
Dialogue: 1,0:04:35.46,0:04:37.17,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,能听到说话声
Dialogue: 1,0:04:37.72,0:04:39.97,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,是在打电话吗
Dialogue: 1,0:04:40.43,0:04:41.97,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,来 啊
Dialogue: 1,0:04:43.35,0:04:46.02,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,今天也吃了好多 我好欣慰
Dialogue: 1,0:04:46.02,0:04:47.27,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,不是电话吧
Dialogue: 1,0:04:49.52,0:04:50.89,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,门没锁
Dialogue: 1,0:04:51.48,0:04:52.90,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,阳菜 我们进来了
Dialogue: 1,0:04:56.32,0:04:57.44,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,你在干什么呢
Dialogue: 1,0:04:57.44,0:04:59.65,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,你们什么时候来的
Dialogue: 1,0:04:59.78,0:05:01.49,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,你背后是什么
Dialogue: 1,0:05:01.49,0:05:03.45,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,有什么吗 没有哦
Dialogue: 1,0:05:09.79,0:05:11.50,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,那该不会是…
Dialogue: 1,0:05:11.87,0:05:12.79,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,乌龟？
Dialogue: 1,0:05:12.79,0:05:13.96,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,不要叫他乌龟
Dialogue: 1,0:05:15.13,0:05:16.17,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,抱… 抱歉
Dialogue: 1,0:05:16.34,0:05:17.96,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,不对 这就是乌龟吧
Dialogue: 1,0:05:18.30,0:05:20.42,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,毫无疑问是乌龟
Dialogue: 1,0:05:20.72,0:05:23.97,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,大家也不喜欢自己被称作人类吧
Dialogue: 1,0:05:24.30,0:05:27.77,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,他有自己的名字 叫龟井先生
Dialogue: 1,0:05:27.77,0:05:28.93,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,龟井先生
Dialogue: 1,0:05:29.31,0:05:31.10,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,对 龟井先生
Dialogue: 1,0:05:31.77,0:05:32.39,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,你看
Dialogue: 1,0:05:32.73,0:05:34.86,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,长得很有沧桑感吧
Dialogue: 1,0:05:35.86,0:05:38.44,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,乌龟不都长这样
Dialogue: 1,0:05:38.69,0:05:40.82,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,都说了不是乌龟
Dialogue: 1,0:05:41.11,0:05:42.45,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,话说 阳菜
Dialogue: 1,0:05:42.45,0:05:44.24,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,宿舍不允许养宠物哦
Dialogue: 1,0:05:45.07,0:05:48.45,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,这么一说 搬进来的时候莉央说过
Dialogue: 1,0:05:48.91,0:05:51.00,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,你应该是知道的吧
Dialogue: 1,0:05:52.54,0:05:55.58,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,但是 龟井先生是我的好朋友
Dialogue: 1,0:05:58.67,0:06:00.80,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,乌龟是好朋友啊
Dialogue: 1,0:06:01.67,0:06:04.55,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,那个 我有什么烦恼的时候
Dialogue: 1,0:06:04.55,0:06:06.39,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,就会找龟井先生商量
Dialogue: 1,0:06:06.76,0:06:09.72,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,感觉跟他可以无话不说
Dialogue: 1,0:06:10.10,0:06:13.44,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,你看 他长得就很像哲学家吧
Dialogue: 1,0:06:13.85,0:06:16.27,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,乌龟都长一个样吧
Dialogue: 1,0:06:16.69,0:06:18.15,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,才没有
Dialogue: 1,0:06:18.40,0:06:20.98,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,但是确实是违反规定了
Dialogue: 1,0:06:22.24,0:06:23.24,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 1,0:06:23.70,0:06:25.86,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,我… 我那个…
Dialogue: 1,0:06:26.16,0:06:29.33,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,没有龟井先生的话 我就不知所措了
Dialogue: 1,0:06:30.37,0:06:33.50,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,那个 我们如果同意的话
Dialogue: 1,0:06:33.50,0:06:36.17,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,可以允许龟井先生住进来吗
Dialogue: 1,0:06:36.58,0:06:37.84,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,穗乃香
Dialogue: 1,0:06:37.84,0:06:39.38,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,怎么这么说 穗乃香
Dialogue: 1,0:06:39.92,0:06:42.34,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,我家里也有养狗
Dialogue: 1,0:06:42.67,0:06:44.84,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,陪我一起长大的
Dialogue: 1,0:06:45.47,0:06:46.80,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,穗乃香
Dialogue: 1,0:06:47.05,0:06:49.43,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,但是 穗乃香离开了狗狗
Dialogue: 1,0:06:49.43,0:06:51.77,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,应该很想念和它一起的生活吧
Dialogue: 1,0:06:54.18,0:06:56.56,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,毕竟狗实在不好带过来
Dialogue: 1,0:06:57.02,0:06:59.94,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,不过 我懂那种难舍难分的感觉
Dialogue: 1,0:07:00.23,0:07:02.61,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,而且龟井先生也不会叫
Dialogue: 1,0:07:03.61,0:07:05.53,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,你们四个人决定吧
Dialogue: 1,0:07:07.16,0:07:09.62,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,你们出演同一部作品
Dialogue: 1,0:07:10.08,0:07:11.95,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,宿舍房间也比较靠近
Dialogue: 1,0:07:12.20,0:07:13.66,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,也算是一个团队了
Dialogue: 1,0:07:14.33,0:07:17.58,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,当然前提是不能给别人添麻烦
Dialogue: 1,0:07:17.79,0:07:19.84,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,你们四个商量决定就好
Dialogue: 1,0:07:21.09,0:07:22.25,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,我们四个…
Dialogue: 1,0:07:22.59,0:07:23.38,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,来决定
Dialogue: 1,0:07:24.09,0:07:27.09,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,我没关系 同意
Dialogue: 1,0:07:27.63,0:07:30.30,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,这位蟹江先生 他凶猛吗
Dialogue: 1,0:07:30.51,0:07:32.93,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,不是蟹江先生啦 是龟井先生
Dialogue: 1,0:07:33.27,0:07:34.52,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,不凶猛哦
Dialogue: 1,0:07:35.02,0:07:36.94,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,那我也同意
Dialogue: 1,0:07:37.73,0:07:38.73,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 1,0:07:39.44,0:07:41.27,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,是吗 那就行了
Dialogue: 1,0:07:41.44,0:07:42.57,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,可以吗
Dialogue: 1,0:07:42.86,0:07:43.90,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,当然
Dialogue: 1,0:07:43.90,0:07:47.99,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,要跟宿舍里其他人 还有之后要搬进来的人确认
Dialogue: 1,0:07:48.32,0:07:49.07,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,记住了吗
Dialogue: 1,0:07:49.32,0:07:49.99,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 1,0:07:50.70,0:07:52.08,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 1,0:07:53.24,0:07:55.25,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,谢谢大家
Dialogue: 1,0:07:56.29,0:07:57.12,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 1,0:07:57.46,0:07:58.29,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,鹤田先生
Dialogue: 1,0:07:58.50,0:07:59.67,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,是龟井先生
Dialogue: 1,0:08:12.89,0:08:15.06,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,龟井先生 你怎么想
Dialogue: 1,0:08:18.44,0:08:19.02,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,来了
Dialogue: 1,0:08:20.52,0:08:21.61,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,舞花
Dialogue: 1,0:08:21.81,0:08:23.07,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,可以进来吗
Dialogue: 1,0:08:23.86,0:08:25.94,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,总感觉睡不着
Dialogue: 1,0:08:25.94,0:08:28.32,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,毕竟明天就要正式录音了
Dialogue: 1,0:08:28.82,0:08:31.82,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,而且还有超有名的声优一起
Dialogue: 1,0:08:31.82,0:08:36.12,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,光是考虑怎么打招呼 就让人操心
Dialogue: 1,0:08:36.45,0:08:38.16,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,志穗和穗乃香呢
Dialogue: 1,0:08:38.46,0:08:39.79,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,已经睡着了
Dialogue: 1,0:08:39.79,0:08:41.38,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,羡慕她们的从容啊
Dialogue: 1,0:08:44.04,0:08:45.34,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,为明天练习呢？
Dialogue: 1,0:08:47.05,0:08:49.88,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,我的角色虽然是无名配角
Dialogue: 1,0:08:50.30,0:08:52.59,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,但我还是想尽全力
Dialogue: 1,0:08:52.84,0:08:55.10,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,所以和龟井先生商量了吗
Dialogue: 1,0:08:56.18,0:08:58.27,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,他听我说了很多
Dialogue: 1,0:08:59.35,0:09:01.77,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,阳菜 来一起练习吧
Dialogue: 1,0:09:02.85,0:09:04.23,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,可以吗 舞花
Dialogue: 1,0:09:05.40,0:09:07.36,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,反正也睡不着
Dialogue: 1,0:09:19.25,0:09:20.75,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,再见了 椿
Dialogue: 1,0:09:21.42,0:09:24.67,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,以你的实力 在那边也绝对没问题
Dialogue: 1,0:09:28.30,0:09:29.17,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,总感觉
Dialogue: 1,0:09:29.38,0:09:32.68,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,这里椿的心情让我有些在意
Dialogue: 1,0:09:33.55,0:09:34.55,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 1,0:09:38.18,0:09:40.81,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,椿的表情真不错啊
Dialogue: 1,0:09:41.52,0:09:44.31,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,这个表情应该配合什么样的演技呢
Dialogue: 1,0:09:46.61,0:09:47.48,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,当然
Dialogue: 1,0:09:48.03,0:09:50.82,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,毕竟我就是我
Dialogue: 1,0:09:52.53,0:09:53.91,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,感觉不错
Dialogue: 1,0:09:54.28,0:09:55.78,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,怎么样 合适吗
Dialogue: 1,0:09:56.12,0:09:57.12,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 1,0:09:57.33,0:10:00.95,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,但是我有点喜欢你刚才的椿
Dialogue: 1,0:10:01.29,0:10:02.25,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 1,0:10:04.04,0:10:05.08,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,真好啊
Dialogue: 1,0:10:05.46,0:10:08.50,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,要是学生A的表情也画出来了就好了
Dialogue: 1,0:10:08.88,0:10:13.18,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,不过你看 她能让椿露出这样的表情
Dialogue: 1,0:10:13.51,0:10:14.51,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,对哦
Dialogue: 1,0:10:15.09,0:10:16.76,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,可以再练一遍吗
Dialogue: 1,0:10:16.76,0:10:17.64,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,当然了
Dialogue: 1,0:10:22.56,0:10:24.44,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,请多关照
Dialogue: 1,0:10:24.90,0:10:26.10,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,要记住哦
Dialogue: 1,0:10:26.10,0:10:28.57,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,这就是录音第一天的气氛
Dialogue: 1,0:10:30.69,0:10:32.15,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 1,0:10:33.07,0:10:34.70,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 1,0:10:35.82,0:10:36.45,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 1,0:10:39.70,0:10:40.66,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,谁来着
Dialogue: 1,0:10:41.29,0:10:43.16,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,原作者和编辑
Dialogue: 1,0:10:44.79,0:10:47.54,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,那么 出演的四个人去打招呼吧
Dialogue: 1,0:10:47.75,0:10:48.42,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 1,0:10:49.13,0:10:52.09,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,首先记得说明自己的角色和名字
Dialogue: 1,0:10:52.38,0:10:53.13,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,明白了吗
Dialogue: 1,0:10:53.55,0:10:54.55,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 1,0:10:56.55,0:10:58.76,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,打扰了 我们是AiRBLUE
Dialogue: 1,0:10:59.18,0:10:59.89,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 1,0:11:02.52,0:11:05.35,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,我是饰演绯车椿的鹰取舞花
Dialogue: 1,0:11:05.73,0:11:07.19,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,请多指教
Dialogue: 1,0:11:07.48,0:11:08.19,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 1,0:11:08.52,0:11:09.69,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,嗯 有劳了
Dialogue: 1,0:11:10.40,0:11:12.98,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,我是饰演凛堂天城的鹿野志穗
Dialogue: 1,0:11:13.65,0:11:15.24,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,请多指教
Dialogue: 1,0:11:15.65,0:11:18.57,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,我是饰演菖蒲彩芽的月居穗乃香
Dialogue: 1,0:11:19.07,0:11:20.49,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,请多指教
Dialogue: 1,0:11:23.33,0:11:27.54,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,那个 我… 我是六石阳菜
Dialogue: 1,0:11:28.25,0:11:29.63,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,请多指教
Dialogue: 1,0:11:32.88,0:11:34.59,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,我是经纪人五十铃
Dialogue: 1,0:11:34.97,0:11:35.84,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 1,0:11:36.88,0:11:39.68,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,还有 我带来了三个人观摩学习
Dialogue: 1,0:11:40.14,0:11:41.26,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,听说了
Dialogue: 1,0:11:41.64,0:11:44.14,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,请坐在入口旁边的沙发
Dialogue: 1,0:11:44.68,0:11:46.06,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 1,0:11:47.27,0:11:49.27,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,打招呼可真好啊
Dialogue: 1,0:11:50.19,0:11:52.52,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,有一种真正的声优的感觉
Dialogue: 1,0:11:52.86,0:11:53.90,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,就是真的
Dialogue: 1,0:11:57.86,0:12:03.33,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,首先有请原作者 无量坂京子老师
Dialogue: 1,0:12:05.79,0:12:06.37,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,老师？
Dialogue: 1,0:12:06.83,0:12:08.12,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,小京 打招呼了
Dialogue: 1,0:12:10.13,0:12:12.29,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,请… 请多关照
Dialogue: 1,0:12:13.04,0:12:14.67,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,请多关照
Dialogue: 1,0:12:15.55,0:12:17.59,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,接下来开始测试
Dialogue: 1,0:12:17.84,0:12:19.72,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,那就麻烦了
Dialogue: 1,0:12:32.27,0:12:34.69,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,在遥远未来的世界某处
Dialogue: 1,0:12:35.61,0:12:41.70,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,这是为一颗球赌上全部青春的少女们的故事
Dialogue: 1,0:12:43.24,0:12:46.37,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,决定全国花球头号队伍的大赛上
Dialogue: 1,0:12:46.66,0:12:50.75,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,现在被视为冠军最有力争夺者的
Dialogue: 1,0:12:51.12,0:12:53.84,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,是圣天蓝学园
Dialogue: 1,0:12:55.25,0:12:58.88,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,火花不过是个常规选手名录上都没有的新人
Dialogue: 1,0:12:59.42,0:13:01.80,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,根本算不上我的对手
Dialogue: 1,0:13:03.26,0:13:06.43,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,激热从去年起成员就没变过啊
Dialogue: 1,0:13:06.77,0:13:09.73,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,战斗力100%解析完毕
Dialogue: 1,0:13:09.94,0:13:12.60,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,胜负已定
Dialogue: 1,0:13:13.19,0:13:17.48,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,今年当然也是圣天蓝夺冠
Dialogue: 1,0:13:26.87,0:13:28.41,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,再见了 椿
Dialogue: 1,0:13:28.79,0:13:31.87,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,以你的实力 在那边也绝对没问题
Dialogue: 1,0:13:32.62,0:13:33.33,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,当然
Dialogue: 1,0:13:33.71,0:13:36.59,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,毕竟 我就是我
Dialogue: 1,0:13:37.67,0:13:39.17,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,可恶啊
Dialogue: 1,0:13:39.17,0:13:40.55,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,社团人数不够
Dialogue: 1,0:13:40.88,0:13:43.01,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,这样都没法参加大赛了
Dialogue: 1,0:13:44.14,0:13:45.80,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,A Part 测试完毕
Dialogue: 1,0:13:46.01,0:13:47.26,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,请稍等
Dialogue: 1,0:13:51.94,0:13:53.73,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,好紧张
Dialogue: 1,0:13:54.02,0:13:55.31,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,刚才是测试
Dialogue: 1,0:13:55.90,0:13:56.61,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,测试？
Dialogue: 1,0:13:57.98,0:14:01.03,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,监督会和大家讨论刚才的测试
Dialogue: 1,0:14:01.03,0:14:02.90,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,然后会提出变更和指令
Dialogue: 1,0:14:02.90,0:14:05.95,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,加入这些变化后 再正式录音
Dialogue: 1,0:14:06.20,0:14:08.12,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,不知道在说什么
Dialogue: 1,0:14:08.12,0:14:09.33,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,真好奇
Dialogue: 1,0:14:19.00,0:14:20.80,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,接下来从头开始
Dialogue: 1,0:14:21.51,0:14:23.55,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,首先是13卡的天城
Dialogue: 1,0:14:25.39,0:14:27.18,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,志穗 提到天城了
Dialogue: 1,0:14:27.97,0:14:28.56,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 1,0:14:28.56,0:14:30.31,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,「百分之百」的地方
Dialogue: 1,0:14:30.89,0:14:33.73,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,「Percent」的「Per」稍微加重一些
Dialogue: 1,0:14:34.10,0:14:35.90,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,百分之百？
Dialogue: 1,0:14:36.31,0:14:36.98,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 1,0:14:37.27,0:14:38.94,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,天城之后也都这样
Dialogue: 1,0:14:39.44,0:14:40.28,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 1,0:14:40.61,0:14:42.11,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,14卡的彩芽
Dialogue: 1,0:14:42.57,0:14:43.19,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 1,0:14:43.49,0:14:44.49,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,单独录音
Dialogue: 1,0:14:45.49,0:14:46.45,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,单独录音…
Dialogue: 1,0:14:47.20,0:14:47.91,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,不知道吗？
Dialogue: 1,0:14:48.49,0:14:49.62,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,知道
Dialogue: 1,0:14:49.62,0:14:51.66,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,就是主线的时候不录吧
Dialogue: 1,0:14:51.66,0:14:52.87,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,明白就好
Dialogue: 1,0:14:53.16,0:14:55.00,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,然后是之后的六花
Dialogue: 1,0:14:55.42,0:14:56.12,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 1,0:14:56.67,0:14:57.63,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,单独录音？
Dialogue: 1,0:14:57.83,0:14:58.67,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,主线？
Dialogue: 1,0:14:59.13,0:15:01.38,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,训练课还没有提到吧
Dialogue: 1,0:15:01.67,0:15:04.38,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,就是紧接着的台词有重叠的部分
Dialogue: 1,0:15:04.38,0:15:08.26,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,录音的时候就分为主线和单独录音
Dialogue: 1,0:15:08.76,0:15:10.93,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,也就是说穗乃香的部分之后录？
Dialogue: 1,0:15:11.22,0:15:11.68,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 1,0:15:12.10,0:15:14.85,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,主线录完之后 在单独录音的时候录
Dialogue: 1,0:15:15.23,0:15:17.65,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,然后 最后要有居高临下的感觉
Dialogue: 1,0:15:17.90,0:15:19.81,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,是 谢谢指导
Dialogue: 1,0:15:19.98,0:15:22.78,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,然后 我看看…
Dialogue: 1,0:15:23.36,0:15:26.61,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,35卡之后的火花
Dialogue: 1,0:15:26.74,0:15:27.49,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 1,0:15:27.95,0:15:31.45,Dial-CH2,,0,0,0,,演技要更加强硬一些
Dialogue: 1,0:15:27.95,0:15:29.57,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,没问题啊
Dialogue: 1,0:15:30.28,0:15:32.41,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,该庆幸吗
Dialogue: 1,0:15:32.91,0:15:33.79,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,我说完了
Dialogue: 1,0:15:33.79,0:15:35.79,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,接下来正式录音
Dialogue: 1,0:15:35.79,0:15:37.25,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,请多指教
Dialogue: 1,0:15:37.96,0:15:39.38,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,正式录音开始
Dialogue: 1,0:15:50.01,0:15:51.05,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,要开始了
Dialogue: 1,0:15:57.81,0:16:01.36,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,火花不过是个常规选手名录上都没有的新人
Dialogue: 1,0:16:01.36,0:16:03.73,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,根本算不上我的对手
Dialogue: 1,0:16:04.15,0:16:07.20,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,激热从去年起成员就没变过啊
Dialogue: 1,0:16:07.57,0:16:10.74,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,战斗力100%解析完毕
Dialogue: 1,0:16:10.87,0:16:15.12,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,今年当然也是圣天蓝夺冠
Dialogue: 1,0:16:27.05,0:16:29.43,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,再见了 椿
Dialogue: 1,0:16:29.76,0:16:33.51,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,以你的实力 在那边也绝对没问题
Dialogue: 1,0:16:35.77,0:16:36.39,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,当然
Dialogue: 1,0:16:36.85,0:16:40.73,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,毕竟我就是我
Dialogue: 1,0:16:43.15,0:16:44.36,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,可恶啊
Dialogue: 1,0:16:44.36,0:16:45.78,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,社团人数不够
Dialogue: 1,0:16:46.23,0:16:48.32,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,这样都没法参加大赛了
Dialogue: 1,0:16:56.12,0:16:58.00,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,好的 主线收录完毕
Dialogue: 1,0:16:58.75,0:17:01.46,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,嗯 有什么问题吗
Dialogue: 1,0:17:01.92,0:17:06.25,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,我看看 18卡开始的学生A和椿
Dialogue: 1,0:17:06.59,0:17:08.30,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,哦 那两个人啊
Dialogue: 1,0:17:08.84,0:17:11.05,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,是不是有点感情投入过多
Dialogue: 1,0:17:11.26,0:17:14.05,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,不 就那样… 那样就好
Dialogue: 1,0:17:15.72,0:17:16.93,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,那样就好
Dialogue: 1,0:17:17.68,0:17:18.68,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,小京
Dialogue: 1,0:17:19.77,0:17:20.77,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 1,0:17:28.11,0:17:30.53,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,18卡开始的椿和学生A
Dialogue: 1,0:17:30.53,0:17:31.74,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,再播放一次
Dialogue: 1,0:17:31.91,0:17:32.49,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 1,0:17:36.79,0:17:38.45,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,再见了 椿
Dialogue: 1,0:17:38.45,0:17:39.08,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 1,0:17:39.08,0:17:42.46,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,以你的实力 在那边也绝对没问题
Dialogue: 1,0:17:43.00,0:17:43.96,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,当然
Dialogue: 1,0:17:44.13,0:17:47.96,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,毕竟我就是我
Dialogue: 1,0:17:51.67,0:17:53.30,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,这样就好吗？
Dialogue: 1,0:17:54.51,0:17:59.14,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,难道说 学生A也是有设定的吗
Dialogue: 1,0:18:00.06,0:18:01.06,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,是有的
Dialogue: 1,0:18:01.56,0:18:02.81,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 1,0:18:03.06,0:18:03.85,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 1,0:18:03.85,0:18:06.02,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,不过连载中没有画
Dialogue: 1,0:18:06.61,0:18:10.57,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,对哦 这表情是这个意思
Dialogue: 1,0:18:11.19,0:18:13.40,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,能再听一遍刚才的部分吗
Dialogue: 1,0:18:13.66,0:18:15.03,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,是 这就播放
Dialogue: 1,0:18:20.58,0:18:22.79,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,再见了 椿
Dialogue: 1,0:18:23.25,0:18:26.33,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,阳菜 是不是我搞砸了呀
Dialogue: 1,0:18:26.33,0:18:28.67,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,感觉会不会是我
Dialogue: 1,0:18:28.67,0:18:30.42,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,还是我们两个
Dialogue: 1,0:18:30.42,0:18:33.88,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,毕竟 我就是我
Dialogue: 1,0:18:36.18,0:18:37.76,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 1,0:18:38.05,0:18:41.64,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,这两个人之间 有着连载中没有讲述的故事啊
Dialogue: 1,0:18:42.02,0:18:42.73,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 1,0:18:43.06,0:18:45.35,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,椿是因为认识了她
Dialogue: 1,0:18:45.35,0:18:47.56,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,才明白了花球的魅力
Dialogue: 1,0:18:47.94,0:18:51.78,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,还有 椿理论家的设定 一定意义上也是…
Dialogue: 1,0:18:51.78,0:18:54.32,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,不好意思 是我们说明不足
Dialogue: 1,0:18:54.61,0:18:55.57,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,哪里哪里
Dialogue: 1,0:18:55.57,0:18:58.87,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,我要是能多解读一下原作就好了
Dialogue: 1,0:18:59.41,0:19:00.62,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,是我的失误
Dialogue: 1,0:19:00.62,0:19:01.41,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 1,0:19:02.00,0:19:02.79,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,哪里
Dialogue: 1,0:19:03.12,0:19:06.12,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,我之前完全没有注意
Dialogue: 1,0:19:06.58,0:19:07.63,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,直到刚才
Dialogue: 1,0:19:10.13,0:19:11.71,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,是啊 通过刚才的表演
Dialogue: 1,0:19:12.34,0:19:14.01,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,嗯 刚才的
Dialogue: 1,0:19:15.05,0:19:16.97,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,有时候就是这样啊
Dialogue: 1,0:19:18.18,0:19:18.97,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,确实
Dialogue: 1,0:19:19.72,0:19:22.06,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,所以 这样就OK了吗？
Dialogue: 1,0:19:22.31,0:19:22.85,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 1,0:19:23.31,0:19:25.02,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,不 重录一遍吧
Dialogue: 1,0:19:25.27,0:19:26.27,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,要录吗？
Dialogue: 1,0:19:26.48,0:19:27.19,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 1,0:19:27.19,0:19:29.36,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,再好好录一次 可以吗
Dialogue: 1,0:19:30.19,0:19:31.40,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,有劳了
Dialogue: 1,0:19:32.36,0:19:34.78,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,18卡开始的椿和学生A
Dialogue: 1,0:19:34.78,0:19:37.36,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,是 对对对… 对不起
Dialogue: 1,0:19:37.36,0:19:39.49,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,是我们演得太夸张了吗？
Dialogue: 1,0:19:40.28,0:19:42.20,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,不 并不夸张
Dialogue: 1,0:19:42.83,0:19:44.20,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,这个方向是正确的
Dialogue: 1,0:19:45.25,0:19:46.25,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,正确？
Dialogue: 1,0:19:46.25,0:19:46.92,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,监督
Dialogue: 1,0:19:47.54,0:19:49.08,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,椿和学生A
Dialogue: 1,0:19:49.33,0:19:52.13,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,就按刚才的感觉 再多投入一些感情
Dialogue: 1,0:19:52.34,0:19:53.76,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,不用在意分镜
Dialogue: 1,0:19:53.76,0:19:55.51,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,之后我们会配合调整
Dialogue: 1,0:19:56.17,0:19:57.72,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,刚才的感觉？
Dialogue: 1,0:19:58.09,0:20:00.22,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,多投入感情…
Dialogue: 1,0:20:00.68,0:20:01.51,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,明白了吗？
Dialogue: 1,0:20:01.80,0:20:02.51,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 1,0:20:03.35,0:20:05.68,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,这一幕的卡 再给我过一遍
Dialogue: 1,0:20:05.98,0:20:06.94,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,明白了
Dialogue: 1,0:20:08.81,0:20:09.90,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,18卡开始
Dialogue: 1,0:20:11.02,0:20:11.77,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,第二次
Dialogue: 1,0:20:18.78,0:20:20.62,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,再见了 椿
Dialogue: 1,0:20:21.45,0:20:24.20,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,以你的实力 在那边…
Dialogue: 1,0:20:25.62,0:20:26.91,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,也绝对没问题
Dialogue: 1,0:20:30.00,0:20:30.79,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,当然
Dialogue: 1,0:20:31.50,0:20:34.88,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,毕竟我就是我
Dialogue: 1,0:20:48.60,0:20:49.64,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,好了 OK
Dialogue: 1,0:20:49.64,0:20:50.52,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,录好了
Dialogue: 1,0:20:51.94,0:20:52.98,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,舞花
Dialogue: 1,0:20:53.15,0:20:53.82,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,阳菜
Dialogue: 1,0:20:54.19,0:20:54.94,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,接下来
Dialogue: 1,0:20:54.94,0:20:57.82,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,回到13卡开始的彩芽 单独录音
Dialogue: 1,0:20:58.44,0:20:59.03,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 1,0:21:00.32,0:21:02.07,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 1,0:21:04.62,0:21:07.12,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,不要让我们担心啦
Dialogue: 1,0:21:07.70,0:21:11.33,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,不过 她们两个演得非常好
Dialogue: 1,0:21:11.67,0:21:13.92,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,声优真好啊
Dialogue: 1,0:21:15.42,0:21:16.50,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 1,0:21:17.71,0:21:18.84,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,好了 OK
Dialogue: 1,0:21:19.26,0:21:20.80,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,A Part 到此结束
Dialogue: 1,0:21:22.68,0:21:24.26,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 1,0:21:27.47,0:21:28.43,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 1,0:21:28.43,0:21:29.23,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 1,0:21:29.81,0:21:31.39,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,是啊 好快
Dialogue: 1,0:21:34.73,0:21:36.94,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,录音还挺累的
Dialogue: 1,0:21:38.36,0:21:40.11,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,我也累得软绵绵了
Dialogue: 1,0:21:41.40,0:21:42.82,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,阳菜 你的
Dialogue: 1,0:21:44.66,0:21:46.28,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,台本软绵绵了
Dialogue: 1,0:21:49.29,0:21:49.91,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,不过…
Dialogue: 1,0:21:50.79,0:21:52.08,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,真开心啊
Dialogue: 1,0:21:52.08,0:21:54.33,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,嗯 太开心了
Dialogue: 1,0:22:01.42,0:22:05.09,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,这里就是 我梦想的地方
Dialogue: 1,0:22:06.14,0:22:07.68,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,小京 你想起来了啊
Dialogue: 1,0:22:08.39,0:22:09.89,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,本来也没忘
Dialogue: 1,0:22:11.14,0:22:11.93,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 1,0:22:12.52,0:22:14.02,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,她叫什么名字来着
Dialogue: 1,0:22:17.90,0:22:18.73,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,桃实
Dialogue: 1,0:22:19.94,0:22:22.57,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,梅之木桃实
Dialogue: 1,0:23:56.08,0:23:58.75,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,下集 「捕捉迎面风」
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,OP “スタートライン”
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.32,0:02:15.07,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,全ては必然だった　このドアの向こうは
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.07,0:02:20.45,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,あの日見てた夢がほら　語りかける
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.45,0:02:25.79,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,思うように出来なくて　笑ったり泣いたりして
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.79,0:02:31.26,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,それでも花が咲いたのは　君がいたから
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.26,0:02:36.84,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,空高く飛ぶ鳥に憧れた
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.84,0:02:42.10,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,届かないものだからって思ってた
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.43,0:02:47.48,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,見上げる青空が眩しすぎて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.48,0:02:49.98,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,目もくらむほど　遠く
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.98,0:02:52.82,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,手を伸ばすほど　高く
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.82,0:02:59.07,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,どこまでも飛んでいけるだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.83,0:03:05.16,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,今始まるここがスタートライン
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.16,0:03:10.17,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,ここにいる自分を信じて
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.17,0:03:16.59,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,聴こえるだろう　本当の心は
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.59,0:03:19.30,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,ずっと君を信じてる
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.30,0:03:21.97,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,いつでもその声が
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.97,0:03:26.27,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,800)}背中を押してくれる
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.32,0:02:15.07,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,在这扇门的背后 一切都是必然
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.07,0:02:20.45,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,你看那曾经的梦想 正要与你对话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.45,0:02:25.79,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,有些事不能如愿 时而欢笑时而流泪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.79,0:02:31.26,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,但花朵依然盛开 是因为身边有你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.26,0:02:36.84,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,展翅高飞的鸟儿让人憧憬
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.84,0:02:42.10,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,因为那是无法触及的高度
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.43,0:02:47.48,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,碧蓝的天空是那么耀眼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.48,0:02:49.98,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,向着令人目眩的远方
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.98,0:02:52.82,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,向着触手可及的高度
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.82,0:02:59.07,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,不论哪里都可以飞得到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.83,0:03:05.16,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,这里就是我们的起点线
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.16,0:03:10.17,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,要相信站在这里的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.17,0:03:16.59,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,你听得到自己的真心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.59,0:03:19.30,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,总是相信着你自己
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.30,0:03:21.97,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,那信赖的话语
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.97,0:03:26.27,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,800)}会永远助你前行
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,ED “はじまりの鐘の音が鳴り響く空”
Dialogue: 1,0:22:30.58,0:22:34.04,ED2-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,480)}I’ll always believe tomorrow
Dialogue: 1,0:22:41.59,0:22:44.97,ED2-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,480)}瞳の奥に映し出す夢が
Dialogue: 1,0:22:44.97,0:22:48.35,ED2-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,480)}前へと進む理由をくれた
Dialogue: 1,0:22:48.35,0:22:53.64,ED2-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,480)}この手に　たくさんの意味をのせて
Dialogue: 1,0:22:54.10,0:22:57.65,ED2-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,480)}忘れかけてた　絆には気づかない
Dialogue: 1,0:22:57.65,0:23:01.15,ED2-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,480)}歩む景色は　霞んで消えてく
Dialogue: 1,0:23:01.15,0:23:03.11,ED2-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,480)}Until you can’t see it
Dialogue: 1,0:23:03.11,0:23:07.37,ED2-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,480)}どんなに汚れたって
Dialogue: 1,0:23:07.37,0:23:13.12,ED2-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,480)}おもちゃ箱に全部詰め込んでいた夢には
